DATABASE MONITOR

	This is a simple daemon to compare DB queries and notify by email.


CONFIGURATION

	All the things you need to specify are in config.yml.sample. Once you want to use it, you need to rename it to config.yml.
  You need to install the adapter gem of your database:
    - if you use postgresql install the gem pg
    - if you use mysql install the gem mysql
    - if you use sqlite install the gem sqlite